  "rationale": "The Features section is designed using Finsweet's 6-layer Client-First hierarchy for maximum scalability and structural clarity. It features a centered header (features_header) followed by a 3-column CSS Grid (features_list) with a 2rem horizontal and 3rem vertical gap, ensuring balanced spacing between the 6 feature cards. Each feature card (features_item) uses a white background and specific padding (3rem 2rem 3.5rem) to create clear separation from the light grey section background. Icons are housed in a fixed-size container (2.1875rem, approx. 35px) as per MAS-V2-007, ensuring consistent visual weight across the grid. All units are in 'rem' to support fluid responsiveness and accessibility. Styles are mapped to global design system variables (color--grey, color--dark-blue, heading-style-h2, heading-style-h6) to maintain architectural integrity."
